{"words":[{"word":"avidius","count":3},{"word":"place","count":2},{"word":"devotion","count":1},{"word":"forgive","count":1},{"word":"seem","count":1},{"word":"forget","count":1},{"word":"hmph","count":1},{"word":"must","count":1},{"word":"aware","count":1},{"word":"rather","count":1},{"word":"underwhelming","count":1},{"word":"performance","count":1},{"word":"tyrannos","count":1},{"word":"hunt","count":1},{"word":"senate's","count":1},{"word":"patience","count":1},{"word":"boundless","count":1},{"word":"reserved","count":1},{"word":"deserve","count":1},{"word":"unless","count":1},{"word":"present","count":1},{"word":"triumph","count":1},{"word":"match","count":1},{"word":"exploits","count":1},{"word":"manes","count":1},{"word":"deep","count":1},{"word":"choice","count":1},{"word":"reconsider","count":1},{"word":"candidacy","count":1},{"word":"septimont's","count":1},{"word":"next","count":1},{"word":"ruler","count":1},{"word":"wake","count":1},{"word":"murmurstown","count":1},{"word":"glory","count":1},{"word":"began","count":1},{"word":"true","count":1},{"word":"arena","count":1},{"word":"yet","count":1},{"word":"entangled","count":1},{"word":"augusta's","count":1},{"word":"petty","count":1},{"word":"concerns","count":1},{"word":"seizing","count":1},{"word":"something","count":1},{"word":"far","count":1},{"word":"greater","count":1},{"word":"dare","count":1},{"word":"groans","count":1},{"word":"pain","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"Such devotion. Forgive me, but you seem to forget your place, Avidius.","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000002},{"text":"Hmph. You must be aware of your rather underwhelming performance during the Tyrannos hunt.","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000002},{"text":"The Senate's patience is not boundless. It's reserved for those who deserve it. Unless you can present a triumph to match your exploits in Manes Deep, we'll have no choice but to... reconsider your candidacy as Septimont's next ruler.","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000002},{"text":"Wake up, Avidius. Isn't Murmurstown the very place where your glory began? That, Avidius, is your true arena.","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000002},{"text":"Yet here you are, entangled in Augusta's petty concerns when you could be seizing something far greater.","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000002},{"text":"How dare you—","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000002},{"text":"*Groans in pain*","quest_name":"By Sun's Burning Hand","quest_id":311000002}]}